duties_responsibilities.duty: Receive and process incoming material, securely and safely store materials, and issue material to work orders and other uses.
Ensure that all necessary transactions are completed in the ERP system and perform cycle counts and analyze inventory discrepancies.
Execute all inventory control activities to meet company business schedules and budgets in a timely and accurate manner.
Implement, execute, and improve cycle count programs, KANBAN systems, etc.
Engage in independent thought and judgment in analyzing problems and recommending methods and techniques for executing job duties in a more cost-effective manner.
Handle day-to-day shipping, receiving, and cycle counting tasks.
Respond creatively to evolving challenges and actively contribute to process improvements.
